239
00:15:33.600 --> 00:15:34.935
Don't get caught on camera.

240
00:15:35.018 --> 00:15:36.270
Or we're screwed.

241
00:15:38.689 --> 00:15:39.606
I'm in.

242
00:15:39.940 --> 00:15:41.024
Tell me your whereabouts.

243
00:15:41.108 --> 00:15:43.444
